Stir boiling water into dry gelatin mix in large bowl until completely dissolved. Add ice; stir until gelatin starts to thicken. Remove any unmelted ice. Add whipped topping; stir with wire whisk until blended. Refrigerate 20 min. or until slightly thickened. Stir in pie filling; spoon into serving bowl. Refrigerate 4 hours or until firm. Store leftovers in refrigerator.